import React from "react";
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import CardContent from '@mui/material/CardContent';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import Stack from '@mui/material/Stack';
import ControlledSwitches from "../components/ControlledSwitches";

function Dashboard() {
    return (
        <Box component="main" sx={{ flexGrow: 1, p: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                Dashboard
            </Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} lg={3}>
                    <Stack spacing={3}>
                        <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                            <CardContent>
                                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                    PUMP Switch
                                </Typography>
                                <ControlledSwitches />
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                        <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                            <CardContent>
                                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                    Device Status
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary">
                                    Online
                                </Typography>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Stack>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} lg={3}>
                    <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                              Sensor Status
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                                This is the content of card 3. It can contain any information you want to display.
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} lg={3}>
                    <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                Timer
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                                This is the content of card 4. It can contain any information you want to display.
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default Dashboard;
